title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Mar 9 2022

description:
Zelensky echoes Churchill in appeal to Europe. New York Times on how the pandemic measures have negatively impacted reading scores. Karol Markowicz talks with Clay and Buck about the lingering mask madness and making everyone who was wrong about lockdowns, masks and vaccines admit they were wrong. C&B take calls.
